headline: Looking at the Narrative for Quest Diagnostics as Growth Outlook and Analyst Views Evolve
summary: Quest Diagnostics has seen its Fair Value Estimate rise slightly, climbing from $188.19 to $191.56 per share as analysts factor in updated growth expectations. This change is supported by increased revenue growth projections, reflecting renewed optimism in the company's outlook following recent research and 2025 guidance updates.
